    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8006-a262-d8e435191791",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, the authors’ proposition is 2-fold. First they want to add more features to the problem level. Second, they introduce an Auto-Encoder to reduce training time and resource requirements. Results show that new model obtains higher accuracies than the regular DKT approach.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-8006-a262-d8e435191791",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
