              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Thus, the authors’ proposition is 2-fold. First they want to add more features to the problem level. Second, they introduce an Auto-Encoder to reduce training time and resource requirements. Results show that new model obtains higher accuracies than the regular DKT approach.",
